ent":"Place red mullet fillets into Varoma dish, making sure some holes remain unobstructed. Insert reserved Varoma tray, place Varoma dish and tray back into position and steam <b>7 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>. Remove Varoma and set aside."},{"content":"Transfer fish stock to a jug. Place 150 g fish stock back into mixing bowl and add cooked red peppers of simmering basket. Blend <b>30 sec\/speed 7<b>. Transfer couscous and red mullet fillets to individual plates. Cover with red pepper sauce and sprinkle with fresh coriander before serving."}],"hintsAndTricks":["This recipe can be made with any type of thin white fish fillets, cut into pieces of approx. 6-8 cm."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","30m","4 portions"]}